        <mj-text align="center" color="#000" font-weight="normal" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 20px 0px">Eres parte de la exclusiva comunidad de <b>ER</b> y por eso, accederás a la preventa en nuestro e-commerce para que compres aplicando descuentos antes que todos.</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section css-class="code" background-color="#ffffff" background-repeat="repeat" background-size="auto" padding="20px 0px 20px 0px" text-align="center" vertical-align="top">
      <mj-column width="300px" padding="20px 20px" border="1px dashed #dddddd">
        <mj-text align="center" color="#000" font-weight="normal" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16px" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 10px 0px">Tu código de descuento es:</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#d5d5d5" font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24px" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px">01ARW10-L19</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-wrapper padding="40px" background-color="#fff">
      <mj-section css-class="banner" background-color="#fff" text-align="center" vertical-align="top" background-url="assets/mail_er/banner.png" background-size="cover" background-repeat="no-repeat">
        <mj-column width="250px">
        </mj-column>
        <mj-column width="250px" padding="50px 0px">
          <mj-text align="center" color="#FFF" font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="22px" line-height="20px" padding="20px 0px">#WhatYouER</mj-text>
          <mj-text align="center" color="#FFF" font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="20px" padding="10px 0px">TEMPORADA VERANO</mj-text>
          <mj-text align="center" color="#FFF" font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="25px" line-height="20px" padding="10px 0px">70 % ON</mj-text>
          <mj-text align="center" color="#FFF" font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="25px" line-height="20px" padding="10px 0px">DESCUENTO</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
    </mj-wrapper>

    <mj-section css-class="social" background-color="#000" padding="30px 0px 0px 0px">
      <mj-group>
        <mj-column width="42%"></mj-column>
        <mj-column width="8%">
          <mj-image href="#" target="_blank" align="center" padding="4px" src="./assets/mail_er/fb-icon.svg" width="26px"></mj-image>
        </mj-column>
        <mj-column width="8%">
          <mj-image href="#" align="center" padding="4px" src="./assets/mail_er/ig-icon.svg" width="26px"></mj-image>
        </mj-column>
        <mj-column width="42%"></mj-column>
      </mj-group>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section css-class="copy" background-color="#000" background-repeat="repeat" padding="20px 0px 30px 0px" text-align="center" vertical-align="top">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#fff" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="15px" padding="0px 25px 5px">EFFORT RESPECT - Todos los derechos reservados 2020</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#A3A3A3" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="14px" line-height="15px" padding="5px 25px">Por favor, no respondas a este mensaje</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
